<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 gẖyr gẖyr sẖkl ạllh kẖạlqny gẖyr sẖkl
 ạ̉nạ bḥṭ nẓạrạt wmạ ktyr bsẖwf bʿyny
 wạ̉nạ bmsẖy mʿ ʿṣạ mạ bsẖwf ạ̉bdaⁿạ bʿyny
 bs ʿnạ ạ̉ṣḥạb ktyr mnḥbn wbyḥbwnạ
 kl wạḥd mnạ gẖyr sẖkl bạlṭbʿ wbạlsẖkl
 wmnsạʿdhn wbysạʿdwnạ klnạ klnạ gẖyr sẖkl
 wạ̉nạ bḥky klmạt wmạ bqdr skt ḥạly
 wạ̉nạ bḥky ạ̹sẖạrạt lạ̉ny mạ bsmʿ ʿḥạly
 wạ̉nạ ktyr zky bạlṣf bs dạymaⁿạ qạʿd ʿkrsy
 wạ̉nạ ktyr sryʿ bạlrkḍ bs mạ ktyr bsẖgẖl rạsy</lyrics>
<title>gẖyr sẖkl</title>
<author>nzạr fạrs, nzạr fạrs</author>
